        "title": "Cold Open",
        "body": "In the largest coordinated action of its kind, the Central Bureau of Investigation raided over 80 locations across 16 states on June 25, 2026, deploying 60 special teams to dismantle a sprawling digital arrest scam network linked to more than 200 cases. Operation Chakra-VI â€” the sixth and most expansive phase of the CBI's cybercrime crackdown â€” resulted in the arrest of two key operatives and exposed a sophisticated modus operandi that included a fake website deceptively mimicking the Supreme Court of India's official domain."
